## Pattern Matching

While LLM mode typically uses a wildcard pattern to handle all events, you can still be selective:

```json
"event_handlers": [
  {
    "event_pattern": "http_request",
    "handler": {"type": "llm"}
  },
  {
    "event_pattern": "websocket_message",
    "handler": {"type": "llm"}
  }
]
```

Most commonly, you'll use:

```json
"event_handlers": [
  {
    "event_pattern": "*",
    "handler": {"type": "llm"}
  }
]
